                            Shape AllReader Plus Version 2.6




AllReader+ is a powerful reading application which allows to read different kinds of text files. AllReader+ supports TXT, HTML, RTF, FB2, PDB/PRC (PalmDOC, zTXT mode 1) and TCR formats.


AllReader+ allows you to view text in Regular or Full screen modes. Also you can rotate the screen to 90, 180, 270 degrees. With the allReader+ you can read books, make bookmarks, save quotes, configure profiles and settings and so on. You can 
even read your favorite books in the night by choosing Day&amp;Night profile!



                     Here are some key features of AllReader Plus:



* Screen rotation to 90, 180, 270 degrees;
* Reading of text files with following formats: TXT, HTML, RTF, FB2, PDB/PRC (PalmDOC, zTXT mode 1), TCR;
* ProfilesDay&amp;Night. Each profile have its own settings for text font, text and background color, status line, etc.;
* Voluntary encoding choice (ANSI, Unicode, UTF-8);
* Regular and Full screen modes;
* Status line including time, battery, pages amount, percentage of read text;
* Status line displaying is adjusted individually for Regular and Full screen modes;
* Scale position in text (on the right or on the bottom of the screen). The scale is adjusted individually for Regular and 
  Full screen modes;
* Joystick buttons are reforming along with screen rotation;
* Regulation of interline interval and symbol spacing;
* Justification;
* 4 types of scrolling: Wave, Line, Smooth and Auto turn pages;
* Auto scrolling feature;
* Bookmarks with navigation along them;
* Search of any text line ignoring hyphenations. Using in search line symbol &quot;?&quot; which is interpreted as any symbol;
* Proper English hyphenation;
* The search is case insensitive;
* Text crossing (by percentage and by pages);
* Quotations keeping;
* File saving as TXT or PDB in voluntary encoding;
* Permanent screen backlight is available;
* allReader+ is digitally signed by Geotrust Global CA certificate.
